<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Anti-Polonism" title="Anti-Polonism">Anti-Polonism</a>, the prejudice against Polish people</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Anti-semitism" class="mw-redirect" title="Anti-semitism">Anti-semitism</a>, the prejudice against Jews</li>
